Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.32,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:05.64,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,So Shinichi-kun acted like he solved \Nthe mystery of the cherry blossom badge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:09.86,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,through reasoning when he \Nactually just saw what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:11.61,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:16.95,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I thought he was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.10,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:24.00,DCMain,SERA,0000,0000,0000,,He just wanted to impress a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.27,DCMain,SERA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:29.51,DCMain,SERA,0000,0000,0000,,it sounds like he wanted to \Nprotect you from your bullies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:31.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.01,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,All I saw through the window \Nthen was a girl who was upset
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:37.49,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,because she had something taken from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.01,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and the word "outsider."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.74,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:46.02,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,in my life that I experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.74,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,solving a heart-pounding mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Even heaven is watching the \Nlabyrinths of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Full throttle reasoning skills \Npenetrate all mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.17,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran and I met in Sakura Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:12.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding in the shadows was \Nan adults' conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:14.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:19.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:54.02,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)}Memories From Sakura Class \N(Shinichi BOY)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Memories From Sakura Class, Shinichi BOY!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:58.33,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop by when I take \NShin-chan to preschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.53,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.29,DCItalic,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to wear a hat \Nand glasses when you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.03,DCItalic,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cause a commotion \Nif people know it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.55,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.81,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.88,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.85,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.38,DCMain,HOLMES,0000,0000,0000,,If one simply knocks out \Nall the central inferences,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.76,DCMain,HOLMES,0000,0000,0000,,and presents one's audience with the \Nstarting-point and the conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:26.26,Sherlock,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sherlock Holmes Series \N{\fs22}The Adventure of \Nthe Dancing Men
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:26.26,DCMain,HOLMES,0000,0000,0000,,one may produce a startling, though \Npossibly a meretricious, effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.85,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.14,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.02,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in the middle of reading this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:39.71,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we're going to \Nyour new preschool today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.90,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.53,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you'll have to \Nwear glasses like Yusaku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.80,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,if you read in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:53.41,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll never wear glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.90,DCMain,FAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fujimine Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.46,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:04.09,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. I'm wearing a hat and glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:09.10,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, ones that scream that you're an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.91,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the cherry blossom name tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.82,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Now stop stealing the spotlight at my event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.02,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:22.90,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, put this on your \Nchest so we can get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.06,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.91,Nametag,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Class \NKudo Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.79,Kindergarten,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}Beika Preschool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:33.99,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The last thing I'd like \Nto ask about is allergies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:36.54,Ronsuke,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Efune Ronsuke (39) \NPreschool Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.89,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is there anything we shouldn't \Nfeed Shinichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.86,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Like eggs, noodles, or cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.55,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,No, not in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.88,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't like raisins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.23,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,He hates them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.85,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.98,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:15.39,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? There's no library.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.20,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're just sleeping in rows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:34.25,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a morgue like the one \NI saw in that movie the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.44,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,This row is Apple Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.82,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,The next row is Tulip Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.52,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,And the top row
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.20,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,is Sakura Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.20,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Good children, good children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:01.84,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who had \Nsomething taken from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.50,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Since her clothes are the \Nonly ones missing a badge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.09,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,she must've had her badge taken from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.10,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,But what's she making?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.91,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.85,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that fold before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:25.63,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fold Dad used to make stars
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.86,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,to decorate the Christmas tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:33.12,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Dad made stars by making \Na straight diagonal cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.54,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,so the curved cut she's making would make...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.62,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,A cherry blossom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.60,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.00,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Since she had her badge \Ntaken from her earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.75,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,she's making a new one out of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.60,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.99,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask her if I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:54.59,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes said if one simply knocks \Nout all the central inferences,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.63,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,and presents one's audience with the \Nstarting-point and the conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.16,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,one may produce a startling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.97,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,though possibly a meretricious effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.02,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.03,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be impressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.32,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.32,DCItalic,BULLY,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone wearing this isn't one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.66,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What was taken from her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.41,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't a plastic badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.04,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.64,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Make me one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:23.42,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.92,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cherry blossom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.95,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she look so puzzled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.57,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.97,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.74,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.43,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.16,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.91,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.19,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:47.64,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Now if I clearly explain \Nto her why I thought that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.74,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,she should be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.80,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.89,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,you lost your cherry blossom badge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:01.00,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,and were crying while \Nmaking a new one, crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.75,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.12,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be surprised like Watson?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.45,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Is she impressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.80,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're all surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.00,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.76,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.72,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.27,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.29,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, I'm not psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:26.09,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Then this girl must be surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:26.77,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.32,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,She's mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.53,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.14,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.40,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,But you were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:34.91,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:36.91,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Were, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.12,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.17,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,She has tears in her eyes right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.87,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:47.88,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disappear while I'm filling \Nout admissions paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.54,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:54.08,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your name tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.18,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You were wearing it a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.97,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.66,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure she \Ndoesn't find the name tag
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.67,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm hiding in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.15,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.04,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.07,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.53,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.64,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.50,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.21,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,we can get you a new name tag,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.58,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,along with Ran-chan's by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.42,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.50,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a cherry blossom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.30,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,you can have this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.80,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.05,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write your name for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.80,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:41.94,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:42.83,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.98,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo Shinichi, Sakura Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.95,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.48,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.21,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:57.33,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:57.99,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.49,Nametag2,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Class \NKudo Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.87,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep it, so promise me, Shinichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:09.37,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a crybaby,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.26,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,so don't call me a crybaby again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.66,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.38,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:20.01,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,And Shinichi-kun, you shouldn't \Ncall people crybabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.51,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.15,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Efune Ronsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.32,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.52,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.15,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.03,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something wrong with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.82,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.10,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Efune-sensei from preschool?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.05,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.87,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.57,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,He has a designated spot for her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.63,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,to sleep during nap time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.13,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,When we go for walks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.93,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,he holds her hand the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.26,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,At the park we went to on our walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:05.18,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,he let her skip the line on the slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.85,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,He calls her name loudly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:11.63,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably planning to win her over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.77,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,and do something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.96,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.65,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,So who's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:18.75,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.33,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.16,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,A-A girl named Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.35,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:32.96,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan, are you sure you're not jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.04,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,because that teacher's giving \NRan-chan all his attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.16,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.64,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.55,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:45.28,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,It is a problem if he's \Nplaying favorites, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.35,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask your teacher why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:47.93,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:53.22,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Ran sleeps closest to the \Nbathroom because one time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.68,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,while she was sleeping far away \Nfrom it, she didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.78,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,He holds her hand on walks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.13,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,because she has a really \Npoor sense of direction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:07.81,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,and once got separated from the \Ngroup and ended up somewhere crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:12.08,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,And he let her slide first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:15.63,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,because she lets everyone go before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:18.46,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,So he has a reason for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.62,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.48,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you say your walking route changed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:25.26,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and you started going to a new park?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.70,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:29.85,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd tell me why \Ntomorrow when we go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.63,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.77,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you just being jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.06,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:41.57,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely looks at her \Nwith the eyes of a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.74,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.40,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:52.87,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi, does Ran-chan sleep \Nlonger than the other kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.30,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.67,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,She always sleeps soundly \Nuntil she's the last one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.80,DCMain,YUKIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, do you have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:09.18,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I have a fan who shares the name \NEfune with Shinichi's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:13.18,Note,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi-kun has a quick mind and \Nsometimes comes into conflict \Nwith the other children, \Nbut he should settle down \Nas he gets accustomed \Nto the preschool. \NLet's wait and see \Nhow he does. \NEfune Ronsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.28,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,She's from Hokkaido, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.19,Years,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,1)}The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.78,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's wrong, Ran-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.19,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.30,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,My mom got mad at me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.87,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,She said I shouldn't be mean to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:23.28,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.11,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been mean to anyone, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.19,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:30.80,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I think you're \Nthe one being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.04,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:50.85,Park,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Children's Park
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.81,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,And the biggest reason I chose this park
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.85,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.50,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.48,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:58.96,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:13:59.89,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.48,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're married?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:31.01,Years,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,420)}Two Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.03,DCMain,TEACHER A,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:04.13,DCMain,TEACHER A,0000,0000,0000,,A black van?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.13,DCMain,TEACHER B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:08.06,DCMain,TEACHER B,0000,0000,0000,,It's been parked outside the rear \Nexit of the preschool for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:12.68,DCMain,TEACHER B,0000,0000,0000,,Should we report it to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.97,DCMain,TEACHER A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:17.48,DCMain,TEACHER A,0000,0000,0000,,We might want to write down its license \Nplate number just in case, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:21.67,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why don't I go check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.90,DCMain,TEACHER B,0000,0000,0000,,Efune-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.04,DCMain,TEACHER A,0000,0000,0000,,Could you do that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.90,DCMain,TEACHER B,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.56,DCItalic,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.53,DCItalic,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.99,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.28,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.04,DCItalic,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.70,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,Reset everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.96,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go better this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.96,DCItalic,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:47.71,DCItalic,WIFE,0000,0000,0000,,There are no time constraints \Nto starting over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:51.02,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.80,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not have this conversation in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.01,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Come sit in the passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.18,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:04.15,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,A simple novelist who's been \Ngaining popularity recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.94,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,A novelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.75,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.62,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,This is my brother-in-law's van.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.80,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my detective friend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.93,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,who was staking out \Nthe place arrested him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.89,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,when he tried to break in through \Nthe preschool's bathroom window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:25.21,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,He's being questioned by \Nthe police right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.82,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Under suspicion of breaking and entering,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.21,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and attempted kidnapping of a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.52,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother-in-law was attempting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:41.60,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,to kidnap a girl named Mori Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:47.11,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Each day you held her hand \Nso your brother-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.86,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,would know which child to kidnap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:54.30,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You called her name loudly \Nand raised her to the top
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.64,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,of the slide near the hospital window
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:17:00.35,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,so your wife could get a good look at her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.50,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and confirm that she was \Nthe child she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:06.65,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,And you had her sleep \Nnext to the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:10.64,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,so she'd be closest when your \Nbrother-in-law broke into the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.10,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't the accident you \Nmentioned as the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.18,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,why she slept near the bathroom happen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:20.76,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,because you'd been slipping her sedatives \Nso she'd be easier to kidnap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:25.09,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Children become confused when given sedatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:30.65,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes do things they don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.51,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You did all of this to make it seem
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.40,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,as though you were favoring her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.03,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,so the other children would resent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:43.19,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and begin bullying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:46.20,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,By writing in her correspondence notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.20,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,that she was bullying other children,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.27,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,you made her parents unfairly lecture her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.76,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,so you'd become the only \Nperson she could depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.63,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:59.46,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,you were attempting to win her over
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:04.06,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,so you'd be able to happily live \Ntogether even after you kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.19,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my son suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.94,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.28,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:14.70,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You actually meant to spend \Nmore time winning her over,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:18.95,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,but you had to rush your plan since \Nmy son nearly discovered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.37,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,But I imagine my son
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:24.87,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,has locked the bathroom \Nwindow after you left,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.87,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,per my instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:31.88,Bathroom,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:31.88,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and is standing in front of \Nthe bathroom door right now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.76,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.78,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,My wife suffers from neurosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:45.39,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,so my brother-in-law and I were forced to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.12,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Because your daughter ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:51.90,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:55.27,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife likely broke down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.68,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,after your daughter ran away from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:00.66,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and wanted to raise a child \Nagain from preschool age,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:05.07,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,when your daughter was cutest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.30,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.68,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,On top of attempting suicide several times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.56,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,she became anorexic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.88,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just watch my \Nwife waste away day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.88,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Could we leave my wife out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:23.22,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,No, your wife should've turned herself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.39,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,into the police by now with your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.98,DCMain,EFUNE,0000,0000,0000,,M-My daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.77,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I have a fan named Efune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.70,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,She had an umbrella with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.98,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,even though she was from Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.49,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,She said it was an old habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:45.50,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Most Hokkaido residents don't \Nuse umbrellas in the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:50.49,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,which means it was likely she grew \Nup somewhere outside Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:55.37,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but she said the last line
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.88,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,of the female detective in the novel \NI wrote felt like it was written for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:14.40,Book,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo Yusaku \NThe Missing Body
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:04.19,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,It's when the detective finds a \Nrunaway who faked their suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.39,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,and tells them there are no time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.98,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,constraints to starting over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.04,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,in order to convince them \Nto return to their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.49,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Since that line left an impression on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:20.90,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she might be a runaway as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:26.12,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to see your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.57,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,turn yourself in before my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.02,DCMain,YUSAKU,0000,0000,0000,,who are waiting nearby lose their patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.38,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,The next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:39.16,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,the preschool children were surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.92,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,to learn Efune-sensei had quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.43,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the kids who liked him cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.68,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:54.06,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry when you feel like it, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.94,DCMain,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I won't call you a crybaby anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:37.08,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,"You can cry when you feel like it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.96,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,What a thing to say for a four year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:42.20,DCMain,SERA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:44.73,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:47.34,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She really didn't like \Nbeing called a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:52.26,DCMain,SERA,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he's been in \Nlove with you since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:53.92,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:58.73,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,His first crush has got \Nto be his actress mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:22:59.84,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.19,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt Ran knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:06.19,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,but since the day we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:07.92,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:11.20,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kudo Shinichi, Sakura Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:14.81,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:17.67,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.67,0:23:19.68,DCItalic,SHINICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:23.03,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:24.00,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:32.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I've been head over heels
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:35.26,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,for that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:42.28,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think she hated \Nme that much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:24:09.05,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:50.46,DCMain,SONOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Makoto-san is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:51.57,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:53.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wear that belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:56.73,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:24:00.83,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for me to give up \Nmy black belt and retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:06.42,DCMain,ASAI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The belt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:09.05,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kyogoku-kun, did you...?
